Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:44.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Spotters report enemy sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:47.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Multiple contacts. Starboard, four o'clock.
